{
    "abstract": "This document defines HTTP fields that support integrity digests. The Content-Digest field can be used for the integrity of HTTP message content.  The Repr-Digest field can be used for the integrity of HTTP representations.  Want-Content-Digest and Want-Repr-Digest can be used to indicate a sender's interest and preferences for receiving the respective Integrity fields.  This document obsoletes RFC 3230 and the Digest and Want-Digest HTTP fields. ",
